{"tid":1565661,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍絲出招企圖對付港台!!! 麻煩幫手檢舉","createTime":"2019-09-13T08:45:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T00:54:50.000Z","uid":43062,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f70de3d37de8a25015ae2157f297515a2cea5e","tid":1565661,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"藍絲企圖對付港台，麻煩幫手檢舉，同埋轉發出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港台報道事實真相，但遭誣陷和打壓，是人民的悲哀。<br />\n港台為左查真相做埋查案個份，仲記唔記得元朗黑夜個集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直以黎就算係政府電台，但係堅持編採自主，唔做官方喉舌，各位麻煩檢舉到呢啲聯署收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請檢舉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeiWLHx7Ao-IsJrBjFq1xNtLjCnPHXWyoSAJqmaTmHdZMN32w/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeiWLHx7Ao-IsJrBjFq1xNtLjCnPHXWyoSAJqmaTmHdZMN32w%2Fviewform&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QbM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=285d1bad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeiWLHx7Ao-IsJrBjFq1xNtLjCnPHXWyoSAJqmaTmHdZMN32w/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手檢舉唔係簽名！</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">拉到最底➡️檢舉濫用情形➡️煽動仇恨、暴力或違法/無禮行為</div>"},{"pid":"304e1221c98145ba86899d5fd2dcb73fe40819ba","tid":1565661,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"睇下做唔做到十連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1/10"},{"pid":"c3ee304e0eb06c039e0a98c09af81dcd746758ac","tid":1565661,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"睇下做唔做到十連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2/10"},{"pid":"3713802934148902e5a6a037fb482349373e7819","tid":1565661,"uid":43062,"like":0,"d